<data>&lt;div class=b&gt;&lt;a href="/"&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/18It"&gt;18It Itivuttakapāḷi&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/18It/1"&gt;1 Ekakanipāta&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/18It/1/1.3"&gt;1.3 Tatiyavagga&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="i"&gt;1.3.1 Pasannacittasutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Ekakanipāta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Tatiyavagga&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Pasannacittasutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_113"&gt; &lt;div class="divNumber"&gt;21.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;113&lt;/span&gt;Vuttañhetaṃ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṃ—  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_114"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;114&lt;/span&gt;“Idhāhaṃ, bhikkhave, ekaccaṃ puggalaṃ pasannacittaṃ evaṃ cetasā ceto paricca pajānāmi—  ‘imamhi cāyaṃ samaye puggalo kālaṃ kareyya yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ sagge’. Taṃ kissa hetu? Cittaṃ hissa, bhikkhave, pasannaṃ. Cetopasādahetu kho pana, bhikkhave, evamidhekacce sattā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjantī”ti. Etamatthaṃ bhagavā avoca. Tatthetaṃ iti vuccati—  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_115"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;115&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;“Pasannacittaṃ ñatvāna,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;ekaccaṃ idha puggalaṃ;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Etamatthañca byākāsi,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;buddho bhikkhūna santike.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_116"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;116&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Imamhi cāyaṃ samaye,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;kālaṃ kayirātha puggalo;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Sugatiṃ upapajjeyya,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;cittaṃ hissa pasāditaṃ.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_117"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;117&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Yathā haritvā nikkhipeyya,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;evamevaṃ tathāvidho;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Cetopasādahetu hi,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;sattā gacchanti suggatin”ti.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_118"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;118&lt;/span&gt;Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="CENTER" id="p_18It_119"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;119&lt;/span&gt;Paṭhamaṃ.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="tn"&gt;&lt;div class=plcb&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="prevP()" id="prevL" name="266884" title="Go to previous page"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt; 1.3 Tatiyavagga&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="upP()" id="upL" name="266884" title="Go to parent page"&gt;up&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="nextP()" id="nextL" name="268397" title="Go to next page"&gt;1.3.2 Mettasutta &amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</data>
